title: WOMAN FINDS PUDDLE OF URINE UNDER SEAT ON BUS 65
text:
WOMAN FINDS PUDDLE OF URINE UNDER SEAT ON BUS 65   Advertisement 
What's worse than stepping into a warm puddle of water? 
Finding out that the puddle was actually a smelly puddle of urine left behind by some inconsiderate commuter on a bus! 
According to a netizen, she found a foul smelling puddle of urine under the seat of a double decker bus 65. She said that the entire cabin smelt of urine and she was shocked to discover the disgusting sight under one of the seats. 
Has anyone else had a similar experience?
